Name: CALPADS
Description: Level 2 validation for CALPADS student information

Rules.Name: Missing birth Country
Rules.Description: Birth Country required If Enrollment Status = 10 (Primary), 20 (Secondary), or 30 (Short-term)
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  EnrollmentStatus.CodeValue EnrollmentStatus
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor EnrollmentStatus ON EnrollmentStatus.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelReasonDescriptorId
where
  Student.BirthCountryDescriptorId IS NULL
  AND EnrollmentStatus.CodeValue in ('10', '20', '30')

Rules.Name: Birthdate after enrollment date
Rules.Description: The birthdate must be before the enrollment date
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryDate,
  Student.BirthDate
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  where
  Student.BirthDate >= StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryDate;

Rules.Name: Enrollment Start Date Greater Than Current Date plus six months
Rules.Description: Enrollment must not be more then 6 months out
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryDate,
  Student.BirthDate
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
where
  dateadd(month, 6, getdate()) < StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryDate

Rules.Name: Missing withdraw date
Rules.Description: Withdraw date is needed if withdraw code is present
Rules.Sql:
select Student.StudentUniqueId,
	  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
	  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate,
	  WithdrawCode.CodeValue WithdrawCode
From edfi.Student
JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation
	ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
JOIN edfi.Descriptor WithdrawCode
	ON WithdrawCode.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId
where StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId IS NOT NULL
and	  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate IS NULL

Rules.Name: exit date before entry date
Rules.Description: Enrollment Exit Date must be greater than or equal to Enrollment Start Date unless the Student Exit Reason Code = N470 (NoShowOther), in which case the date must be on or one day prior to the Start Date
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  ssa.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  ssa.ExitWithdrawDate,
  ssa.EntryDate,
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue WithdrawCode
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ssa ON Student.StudentUSI = ssa.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor WithdrawCode ON WithdrawCode.DescriptorId = ssa.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId
where
  ssa.ExitWithdrawDate < ssa.EntryDate
  AND NOT (
    WithdrawCode.CodeValue = 'N470'
    and (
      ssa.ExitWithdrawDate = ssa.EntryDate
      OR dateadd(day, 1, ssa.ExitWithdrawDate) = ssa.EntryDate
    )
  );

Rules.Name: Enrollment Exit Date Greater Than Current Date plus 30 days
Rules.Description: Withdraw date must not be more than 30 days
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor EnrollmentStatus ON EnrollmentStatus.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelReasonDescriptorId
where
  dateadd(day, 30, getdate()) < StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate

Rules.Name: Missing withdraw code
Rules.Description: Withdraw code is needed if withdraw date is present
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate,
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue WithdrawCode
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor WithdrawCode ON WithdrawCode.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId
where
  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId IS NULL
  and StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate IS NOT NULL

Rules.Name: E150 exit requires new enrollment at same school within 1 day
Rules.Description: If Exit Code equals E150, then Enrollment Start Date (at same school) cannot be greater than 1 day after Enrollment Exit Date
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  ssa.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  ssa.ExitWithdrawDate,
  ssa.EntryDate,
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue WithdrawCode
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ssa ON Student.StudentUSI = ssa.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor WithdrawCode ON WithdrawCode.DescriptorId = ssa.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId
where
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue = 'E150'
  AND ssa.ExitWithdrawDate < ssa.EntryDate
  AND dateadd(day, 1, ssa.ExitWithdrawDate) > ssa.EntryDate

Rules.Name: E155 Exit valid only  between May 15 - Aug. 15
Rules.Description:
If Exit Code equals E155, 
then Enrollment Exit Date must be between May 15 and August 15
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  ssa.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  ssa.ExitWithdrawDate,
  ssa.EntryDate,
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue WithdrawCode
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ssa ON Student.StudentUSI = ssa.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor WithdrawCode ON WithdrawCode.DescriptorId = ssa.ExitWithdrawTypeDescriptorId
where
  WithdrawCode.CodeValue = 'E155'
  AND (
    FORMAT (ssa.ExitWithdrawDate, 'MM-dd') < '05-15'
    OR FORMAT (ssa.ExitWithdrawDate, 'MM-dd') > '08-15'
  )

Rules.Name: Enrollment Status cannot equal 50 for AD Grade Level
Rules.Description: When Grade Level is AD, Enrollment Status cannot equal 50.
Rules.Sql:
select
  Student.StudentUniqueId,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolId AS EducationOrganization,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.ExitWithdrawDate
From
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation ON Student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor GradeLevel ON GradeLevel.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelDescriptorId
  JOIN edfi.Descriptor entryCode ON entryCode.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryTypeDescriptorId
where
  GradeLevel.CodeValue = 'AD'
  and entryCode.CodeValue = '50'
Rules.ExternalRuleId: Enrollment Status cannot equal 50 for AD Grade Level

Containers.Name: STUDENT INFORMATION
Containers.Description: Rules for the Student Information Submission

Rules.Name: Student ID length
Rules.Description: Student ID should not be more than 15 characters.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  LEN(StudentUniqueId) > 15;

Rules.Name: Student first name length
Rules.Description: Student first name should not be more than 15 characters.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT StudentUniqueId,
		SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
		 Student.FirstName,
		 Student.MiddleName,
		 Student.LastSurname,
		'School' as Discriminator
FROM edfi.Student
JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation
	on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE LEN(Student.FirstName) > 30;

Rules.Name: Student middle name length
Rules.Description: Student first name should not be more than 15 characters.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  Student.FirstName,
  Student.MiddleName,
  Student.LastSurname,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  LEN(Student.MiddleName) > 30;

Rules.Name: Student last name
Rules.Description: Student last name should not be more than 15 characters.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  Student.FirstName,
  Student.MiddleName,
  Student.LastSurname,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  LEN(Student.LastSurname) > 30;

Rules.Name: Student  name suffix length
Rules.Description: Student name suffix should not be more than 3 characters.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT StudentUniqueId,
		SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
		 Student.FirstName,
		 Student.MiddleName,
		 Student.LastSurname,
		 Student.GenerationCodeSuffix,
		'School' as Discriminator
FROM edfi.Student
JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation
	on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE LEN(Student.GenerationCodeSuffix) > 3;

Rules.Name: School Year missing from enrollment
Rules.Description: School Year is mandatory
Rules.Sql:
SELECT StudentUniqueId,
		SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
		 SchoolYear,
		'School' as Discriminator
FROM edfi.Student
JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation
	on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE StudentSchoolAssociation.SchoolYear IS NULL;

Rules.Name: student missing gender
Rules.Description: Student is missing gender
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  SchoolYear,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  student.BirthSexDescriptorId IS NULL;

Rules.Name: student missing birth country
Rules.Description: Student is birth country
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  SchoolYear,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  student.BirthCountryDescriptorId IS NULL;

Rules.Name: Student age out of bounds
Rules.Description: Student age is over 22 for non-adult education, or adult education and less than 16 or more than 80
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  *
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      StudentUniqueId,
      SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
      birthdate,
      datediff(year, birthdate, getdate()) age,
      'School' as Discriminator,
      CodeValue as Grade
    FROM
      edfi.Student
      JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
      JOIN edfi.descriptor on Descriptor.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelDescriptorId
  ) as tab1
WHERE
  (age > 22)
  OR (
    Age < 16
    AND Grade in ('Adult Education', 'AD')
  )
  OR (
    Age > 80
    AND Grade in ('Adult Education', 'AD')
  )

Rules.Name: Enrollment Start Date Less Than Birth Date
Rules.Description: Enrollment Start Date Less Than Birth Date
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  birthdate,
  StudentSchoolAssociation.entryDate,
  'School' as Discriminator
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
WHERE
  birthdate > EntryDate

Rules.Name: Invalid age for Kindergarten (KN) student
Rules.Description: Invalid age for Kindergarten (KN) student
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  *
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      StudentUniqueId,
      SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
      birthdate,
      datediff(year, birthdate, getdate()) age,
      'School' as Discriminator,
      GradeDescriptor.CodeValue as Grade
    FROM
      edfi.Student
      JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
      JOIN edfi.descriptor GradeDescriptor on GradeDescriptor.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelDescriptorId
      LEFT JOIN edfi.StudentSpecialEducationProgramAssociation ON StudentSpecialEducationProgramAssociation.StudentUSI = Student.StudentUSI
    WHERE
      StudentSpecialEducationProgramAssociation.StudentUSI is null
  ) as tab1
WHERE
  (
    age < 4
    or age > 7
  )
  AND Grade in ('Kindergarten', 'KN')

Rules.Name: Invalid Student Age for Student Initial US School Enrollment Date K-12
Rules.Description: If Student Initial US School Enrollment Date K-12 is populated, then student age as of that date must be at least 4 years.
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  *
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      StudentUniqueId,
      SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
      birthdate,
      datediff(
        year,
        birthdate,
        StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.USInitialSchoolEntry
      ) ageAtEntry,
      'School' as Discriminator,
      GradeDescriptor.CodeValue as Grade,
      StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.USInitialSchoolEntry
    FROM
      edfi.Student
      JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
      JOIN edfi.descriptor GradeDescriptor on GradeDescriptor.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelDescriptorId
      JOIN edfi.StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation ON StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.StudentUSI = Student.StudentUSI
  ) as tab1
WHERE
  ageAtEntry < 4;

Rules.Name: Missing Student Initial US School Enrollment Date
Rules.Description: If 1) Student Grade Level Code = KN, 01, 02, 03, 04, 05, 06, 07, 08, 09, 10, 11, 12, UE, US AND 2) a) Student Birth Country Code not equal to US or PR or b) English Language Acquisition Status = EL Then Student Initial US School Enrollment Date must be populated
Rules.Sql:
SELECT
  StudentUniqueId,
  SchoolId as EducationOrganizationId,
  'School' as Discriminator,
  GradeDescriptor.CodeValue as Grade,
  StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.USInitialSchoolEntry,
  CountryDescriptor.CodeValue as BirthCountry
FROM
  edfi.Student
  JOIN edfi.StudentSchoolAssociation on student.StudentUSI = StudentSchoolAssociation.StudentUSI
  JOIN edfi.descriptor GradeDescriptor on GradeDescriptor.DescriptorId = StudentSchoolAssociation.EntryGradeLevelDescriptorId
  JOIN edfi.descriptor CountryDescriptor on CountryDescriptor.DescriptorId = Student.BirthCountryDescriptorId
  LEFT JOIN edfi.StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation ON StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.StudentUSI = Student.StudentUSI
WHERE
  GradeDescriptor.CodeValue IN (
    'KN',
    '01',
    '02',
    '03',
    '04',
    '05',
    '06',
    '07',
    '08',
    '09',
    '10',
    '11',
    '12',
    'UE',
    'US'
  )
  AND StudentMigrantEducationProgramAssociation.USInitialSchoolEntry IS NULL;
